    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The row of small twists or rolls at the base of a hand-sewn headband formed by passing one thread over the top of the other.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
